        throws java.lang.Exception
        ValueBiBinaryOperator.apply(T, U, T, U) equivalent which declares a throws clauses, allowing exceptions to be caught outside of lambda context. Like other interfaces of this package, this interface implements a java corresponding interface. All exceptions which occurs inside the lambda is rethrown in the implemented method using RethrowException.rethrow(Throwable).
